  m_Text: "\xA9 2018 in2sight GmbH. All rights reserved. game4automation\xAE is a
    registered trademark.\n\nrealvirtual.io (formerly game4automation) is a framework
    based on Unity to simplify automation design, 3d visualization of automation
    concepts and virtual commissioning. It is developed and maintained by in2sight
    GmbH. \n\nThis product bundles Sharp7,  Copyright (C) 2016 Davide Nardella. It
    is licensed by Davide Nardella to in2sight GmbH under the Apache 2.0 license.
    For details on Sharp7 see http://snap7.sourceforge.net/ \n\nin2sight is providing
    additional services and solutions like training, support, direct CAD Integrations,
    additional automation interfaces and individual solutions based on Unity.\n\nUse
    the middle and right mouse button or touch with your fingers on mobile devices
    to navigate in this demo scene. \n\nLet's change the game. \n\nhttps://realvirtual.io\n"
